Great inexpensive app with good real sound ! My main criticism is that it has 70% of the licks at shape 1(or position 1 if you prefer), 25 % at shape 3, and occasionally 5% to the other positions. For example, position 4 (root at 5th string A shape bar chord) is neglected this is too bad, especially for the keys of E, F, and even G, for guitars without a cutaway (or acoustic guys who can do bends). That's why i rate four stars. Too bad almost perfect !

I'm having a lot of fun playing different styles of blues music on my guitar! For a long while I use to play only rock music. This app expanded my horizons about the blues on guitar. Thank you, Jonathan Bell! Sincerely, Billy
